<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 20:07:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>我是以色列军事情报局的心理学家。这就是为什么单位总是出错的原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-was-a-psychologist-at-israels-military-intelligence-heres-what-its-doing-wrong/0000018c-26c2-d04a-af9f-f6f2b8500000</link><description>当我被军事情报局聘用时，我被告知他们对我在跨文化心理学方面的工作感兴趣。我发现的是一个身体，它被自己的内部文化所束缚，以至于它无法倾听相反的声音</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 19:51:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-was-a-psychologist-at-israels-military-intelligence-heres-what-its-doing-wrong/0000018c-26c2-d04a-af9f-f6f2b8500000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列通知阿拉伯国家，希望在战后加沙建立缓冲区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/israel-informs-arab-states-it-wants-buffer-zone-in-postwar-gaza-sources-say/0000018c-268e-d04a-af9f-f6be18c70000</link><description>据地区安全官员称，缓冲区的目的是防止未来的袭击，作为加沙非军事化计划的一部分。美国官员重申，他们“不会支持缩小加沙的地理限制”</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 19:10:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/israel-informs-arab-states-it-wants-buffer-zone-in-postwar-gaza-sources-say/0000018c-268e-d04a-af9f-f6be18c70000</guid></item><item><title>应对恐怖袭击期间杀害平民的以色列士兵：我们开枪直到他们倒下</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-who-killed-civilian-during-response-to-attack-we-shot-until-they-fell/0000018c-25c7-dc03-a9ec-3dff4f720000</link><description>辛贝特、警方和宪兵正在调查一名以色列平民的死亡事件。枪杀他的士兵告诉电视采访者，“每个士兵都渴望检查这个盒子”</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 16:45:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-who-killed-civilian-during-response-to-attack-we-shot-until-they-fell/0000018c-25c7-dc03-a9ec-3dff4f720000</guid></item><item><title>以色列著名政治学家、杰出犹太复国主义学者什洛莫·阿维内里 (Shlomo Avineri) 去世，享年 90 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/shlomo-avineri-renowned-israeli-political-scientist-eminent-zionist-scholar-dies-at-90/0000018c-2540-d04a-af9f-f5f2c9e60000</link><description>阿维内里是世界上最重要的马克思和黑格尔著作、犹太复国主义和社会主义研究者之一，也是一位多产的作家和记者。他对西方民主国家面临的挑战提出警告，称“我们仍未成功找到应对这些挑战的工具”</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 12:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/shlomo-avineri-renowned-israeli-political-scientist-eminent-zionist-scholar-dies-at-90/0000018c-2540-d04a-af9f-f5f2c9e60000</guid></item><item><title>“他们被下了药”：被释放的以色列人质的亲属讲述哈马斯被囚禁的恐怖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/they-were-drugged-relatives-of-freed-israeli-hostages-channel-hamas-captivity-horror/0000018c-24c7-dc03-a9ec-3cff21210000</link><description>一名兽医正在对枪伤进行手术；一名八岁的孩子在枪林弹雨中挨家挨户跑；一位母亲不知道她三岁的女儿是死是活。随着人质返回以色列，哈马斯被囚禁的证词浮出水面</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 10:16:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/they-were-drugged-relatives-of-freed-israeli-hostages-channel-hamas-captivity-horror/0000018c-24c7-dc03-a9ec-3cff21210000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战火重燃，卡塔尔斡旋恢复以色列与哈马斯停火谈判继续进行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/as-gaza-fighting-renews-qatari-mediated-talks-to-return-israel-hamas-cease-fire-carry-on/0000018c-247a-ded2-abff-ad7e51460000</link><description>以色列和哈马斯未能就周五晚上释放人质名单达成协议；卡塔尔证实谈判仍在进行中，并补充说以色列对加沙的轰炸使调解努力“复杂化”</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 09:31:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/as-gaza-fighting-renews-qatari-mediated-talks-to-return-israel-hamas-cease-fire-carry-on/0000018c-247a-ded2-abff-ad7e51460000</guid></item><item><title>基辛格的权力高于进步的范式在以色列引起了注意</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/kissingers-power-over-progress-paradigm-found-attentive-ears-in-israel/0000018c-21c0-d21c-abae-77fca3810000</link><description>亨利·基辛格比其他任何人都更明确地规定了以色列在美国外交政策中的特殊地位，即以色列可以免于遵守美国要求他国制定的规范。他的做法与以色列的外交政策一致</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 04:00:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/kissingers-power-over-progress-paradigm-found-attentive-ears-in-israel/0000018c-21c0-d21c-abae-77fca3810000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡回归本源，但他的新口号已经过了保质期</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-goes-back-to-basics-but-his-new-slogan-has-already-passed-its-sell-by-date/0000018c-21db-d9ef-abcd-3ffb69860000</link><description>多年来帮助和怂恿哈马斯的以色列总理传达了一个新信息：只有他才能阻止巴勒斯坦建国。战争</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 04:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-goes-back-to-basics-but-his-new-slogan-has-already-passed-its-sell-by-date/0000018c-21db-d9ef-abcd-3ffb69860000</guid></item><item><title>释放人质是以色列政府对 10 月 7 日惨败的部分赎罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/hostage-release-is-israeli-governments-partial-atonement-for-the-october-7-fiasco/0000018c-21be-da36-a1de-67bffb610000</link><description>现在，哈马斯扣押的人质几乎一半已被释放，预计以色列将重返地面行动 — — 以及面临的困境：下一步该尝试释放谁以及以什么价格？</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 04:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/hostage-release-is-israeli-governments-partial-atonement-for-the-october-7-fiasco/0000018c-21be-da36-a1de-67bffb610000</guid></item><item><title>向以色列南部和中部发射猛烈火箭弹；哈马斯扣押的六名人质已确认死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article-live/six-more-israeli-hostages-freed-from-gaza-report-truce-extended-for-another-day/0000018c-2367-d4e6-affd-2f675df00000</link><description>以色列国防军拦截从加沙地带向以色列边境社区发射的火箭 以色列称哈马斯拒绝公布周五从加沙释放的人质，违反了停火协议 巴勒斯坦人报告称，以色列对加沙的袭击造成数十人死亡 卡塔尔继续与以色列接触双方称，以色列的轰炸使新的停火努力“复杂化”。 ■ 休战第七天，八名以色列人获释。 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列境内至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵被杀；加沙仍有超过 159 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：加沙至少有 14,000 人死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 03:36:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article-live/six-more-israeli-hostages-freed-from-gaza-report-truce-extended-for-another-day/0000018c-2367-d4e6-affd-2f675df00000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-12-01/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-2257-d21c-abae-76ffa5890000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 22:42:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-12-01/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-2257-d21c-abae-76ffa5890000</guid></item><item><title>“即使在整个战争中，我实际上更喜欢以色列人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-12-01/ty-article/.highlight/even-within-this-whole-war-i-actually-like-israelis-more/0000018c-2248-dc03-a9ec-3e7b1af00000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名低音提琴手解释了在如此痛苦的时刻演奏音乐的感觉，一名酒店工作人员离开一个战区前往另一个战区</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 22:34:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-12-01/ty-article/.highlight/even-within-this-whole-war-i-actually-like-israelis-more/0000018c-2248-dc03-a9ec-3e7b1af00000</guid></item><item><title>红十字会必须走</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-red-cross-must-go/0000018c-21c7-d9ef-abcd-3fe7a3380000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 22:12:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-red-cross-must-go/0000018c-21c7-d9ef-abcd-3fe7a3380000</guid></item><item><title>我在与哈马斯的战争中失去了我的儿子。武力和暴力不是解决问题的办法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-lost-my-son-to-the-war-with-hamas-force-and-violence-arent-the-solution/0000018c-21f1-dc03-a9ec-3dfb54630000</link><description>七百万犹太人可以用暴力永远统治数百万巴勒斯坦人，而不会付出失去民主的高昂代价——或者对我来说，失去我心爱的第一个孩子——的想法是一种幻想。 10月7日破灭的幻想</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 22:09:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-lost-my-son-to-the-war-with-hamas-force-and-violence-arent-the-solution/0000018c-21f1-dc03-a9ec-3dfb54630000</guid></item><item><title>可以挽救内塔尼亚胡遗产的一举一动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-one-move-that-can-save-netanyahus-legacy/0000018c-21e1-da36-a1de-67e7a2fc0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 21:58:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-one-move-that-can-save-netanyahus-legacy/0000018c-21e1-da36-a1de-67e7a2fc0000</guid></item><item><title>否认哈马斯的暴行是其对以色列进行心理虐待的又一个阶段</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/denial-of-hamas-atrocities-is-another-stage-in-its-psychological-abuse/0000018c-21e1-d9ef-abcd-3fe19f370000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 21:40:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/denial-of-hamas-atrocities-is-another-stage-in-its-psychological-abuse/0000018c-21e1-d9ef-abcd-3fe19f370000</guid></item><item><title>停止本-格维尔枪支表演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/stop-the-ben-gvir-gun-show/0000018c-21e1-dc03-a9ec-3dfba0030000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 21:16:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/stop-the-ben-gvir-gun-show/0000018c-21e1-dc03-a9ec-3dfba0030000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔的部门偷工减料向以色列人发放持枪许可证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-ministry-cuts-corners-to-issue-gun-permits-to-israelis/0000018c-21be-d21c-abae-77beee350000</link><description>以色列一名高级安全官员表示，这种行为会酿成灾难。 “他们像分发糖果一样分发枪支。枪支许可证不是儿童游戏。该部几乎没有监督”</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 20:49:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-ministry-cuts-corners-to-issue-gun-permits-to-israelis/0000018c-21be-d21c-abae-77beee350000</guid></item><item><title>一次又一次的证词揭露了哈马斯强奸以色列妇女活动的范围</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/hamas-campaign-of-rape-against-israeli-women-is-revealed-testimony-after-testimony/0000018c-2144-da36-a1de-6767dac90000</link><description>Cochav Elkayam-Levy 博士和她的民事委员会收集的证据汇总了一幅不容置疑的可怕景象：10 月 7 日，哈马斯恐怖分子有系统地实施了强奸和性虐待行为。然而她发现，国外并不急于承认这一点</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 20:24:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/hamas-campaign-of-rape-against-israeli-women-is-revealed-testimony-after-testimony/0000018c-2144-da36-a1de-6767dac90000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷恐怖袭击引发加沙战斗蔓延的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/the-jerusalem-terror-attack-raises-concerns-about-the-spillover-of-fighting-from-gaza/0000018c-208a-d9ef-abcd-3eab91230000</link><description>耶路撒冷发生的致命恐怖袭击为以色列国家安全部长提供了推动其枪支分配政策的弹药，从而强化了最终鼓励极端分子的反馈循环</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 20:15:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/the-jerusalem-terror-attack-raises-concerns-about-the-spillover-of-fighting-from-gaza/0000018c-208a-d9ef-abcd-3eab91230000</guid></item></channel></rss>